<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1128492-right-at-the-end-when-bart-is-reading">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Right at the end when Bart is reading Malcolm's journal and Cathy says it's blank and the real one was burnt in a fire, does she mean the recent fire or the fire at foxworth hall years before, in which case the journal Bart had would be always been blank? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
