<span id="freeTextContainer17850773882779682544">This book was a hot mess....And I loved it! <br/><br/>I read a review that said this book &quot;went off the rails&quot; <br/><br/>but come on y&apos;all! <br/><br/>The Dollanganger series was never on the rails, so how could it go off them. <br/><br/>Nothing in If There Be Thorns is realistic but that&apos;s what makes it great! <br/><br/>Who wants to read about real life during these times we&apos;re living through? <br/><br/>I want to read some messy shit! <br/><br/>I want to laugh out loud at how wild this family is. <br/><br/>If There Be Thorns is book 3 in The Dollanganger series which starte</span>
  <span id="freeText17850773882779682544" style="display:none">This book was a hot mess....And I loved it! <br /><br />I read a review that said this book "went off the rails" <br /><br />but come on y'all! <br /><br />The Dollanganger series was never on the rails, so how could it go off them. <br /><br />Nothing in If There Be Thorns is realistic but that's what makes it great! <br /><br />Who wants to read about real life during these times we're living through? <br /><br />I want to read some messy shit! <br /><br />I want to laugh out loud at how wild this family is. <br /><br />If There Be Thorns is book 3 in The Dollanganger series which started with Flowers in the Attic. That book is about 4 siblings who are forced to live in their grandparents attic and its a wild ride y'all! <br /><br />V.C. Andrews isn't for everyone. Her stories are dark and usually include abuse and/or incest. But Andrews sure knew how to tale a story. <br /><br />No rec because either you're a V.C. Andrews fan or you're not!</span>
